{"tid":2233681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英指如涉事教職員犯事時國安法已生效應國安法伺候","createTime":"2020-10-07T10:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T10:18:15.000Z","uid":156254,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f09bbd6a53681261017e5bcd68fd80ea1fb6e35","tid":2233681,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"梁振英指如涉事教職員犯事時國安法已生效應國安法伺候<br />\n2020-10-07 HKT 17:59<br />\n 分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n馮卓垣報道<br />\n九龍塘宣道小學一名教師被指有計劃地散播港獨，教育局以嚴重專業失德為由，取消該名教師的註冊。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英表示，如果涉事老師及校長犯事時，《港區國安法》已生效的話，就要被「國安法伺候」。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，在「香港是中國不可分割的一部分」這事上，學校沒有政治中立的餘地。<br />\n<br />\nPK 689<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c4bac16c6f5c966888497aec0fdda57f28e48d","tid":2233681,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"個時未生效<br />\n炒乜撚"},{"pid":"e618f66605f459b6bac926a9ad1bfdcff45da535","tid":2233681,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"咪撚理條失業廢老"},{"pid":"aefe7863b50bbef711b22dbdc80c71fcdc5993fe","tid":2233681,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"呢單無100%證據都可以講到當事人有做過咁<br />\n其實全香港學校既人係咪都已經夠潛質去申請政治庇護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229f8967fa5ab685e618c333d65f23069d38c35e","tid":2233681,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e618f66605f459b6bac926a9ad1bfdcff45da535","tid":2233681,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-